<p>
The pav:api exposes playlist data. It is under development and currently supports the following url patterns. More to come.
</p>
<p>
Return type can either be infered by content negotiation (by setting request Accept header to 
desired content type), by appending the content type to the url (.html, .xml, .json) or by adding ?format=(html, xml, json) to the query parameter. JsonP for cross-domain access is delivered to requests with callback param. Default return type is currently html but will change to json when the api is put in production.
</p>

